      "Your AI assistant can instantly answer questions about destinations, prices, or packages — even outside office hours.",
    icon: "bx:bxs-plane-alt",
  },
  {
    title: "Convert More Visitors",
    description:
      "Turn website visitors into real leads. The chatbot guides them from curiosity to booking without needing to call or wait.",
    icon: "bx:bxs-conversation",
  },
  {
    title: "Always Available 24/7",
    description:
      "Let clients chat anytime — your AI assistant never sleeps. Perfect for answering questions while you focus on sales.",
    icon: "bx:bxs-time-five",
  },
  {
    title: "Easy Integration",
    description:
      "Add the chat widget to your existing website in minutes. Works with any site or CMS — no coding required.",
